  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "28 new features. 78 bug fixes. 4 improvements.",
      "checksum": "sha256:17b1a680f6c75c04b0f1e0bed9e71a96cef58031259f7c15d7ea5266c5017e05",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "The biggest pass landed on M C P stability, and your hooks just got a lot smarter.",
      "checksum": "sha256:da1ea1e7b79ff0e8f798888b423f2463567d01c4736bba4e9f3c6ba81e3564fa",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 8
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "First. Hooks now read the active effort level.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ab9494f2181b76b0390badfc2c4ea433ebc88a62c1ed7dd6a11e3bafa032efff",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 25
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "The CLAUDE EFFORT environment variable flows into hooks and into every Bash subprocess.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fc7ef090aa557171d69ecae7385970536f7889a293f3ff5bbda7c82002729ce5",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 5.015510204081632,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 33
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Adapt your logging or skip expensive work when you are on low effort.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d40695a2573f3f83aef0f475a07be319d26f422e0db4deb866d600d832b1b567",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 46
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "CI integrations finally get the context they always needed.\n\nSecond.",
      "checksum": "sha256:959fa3a36f9fa3fd49bcf8b1a41ec217c005202fefb6c74ea83e6d1ae9f5c63a",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 59
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "The dash dash plugin URL flag fetches a plugin zip archive directly from any URL.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6775a44d525e7f1f90a23b70f9260c4c200fa7c48c2bf0c1cc5a189d290a1c8e",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 69
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Session scoped, zero install, zero footprint.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5c33c01a798ca6b1f1bbedbdeeb1b4faae78784e76a0e60353748c0d7c150b5d",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 86
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Try a plugin in seconds and toss it when you are done.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b8e2ae8b76d28b4d4fdfda9e9a49ab85bd7ecbebcef6e14fe90163ebcaae1689",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 92
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Third. Set CLAUDE CODE DISABLE ALTERNATE SCREEN to one and your conversation stays in the terminal's native scrollback.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ec7d0557c22be35da23c9ddf0e2b50e110d801f16838c535e3ef2921b98a3c99",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 7.569705215419501,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 105
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "No more fullscreen alternate screen swap.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f97ea039619d06b98ac23a868569f09cedf1660da7c2dcb58847efebf501b03d",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 2.136235827664399,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 123
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Your output is right there in the history where you can search it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:84062a883f8d165fe9f536c4e65aac6488b0d95f98c1e8d3097e4d6407e57cff",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 129
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Fourth. Subagents finally discover project, user, and plugin skills through the Skill tool again.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5e2fd6776ac8026fd5e79e82aa1b2a8d4860738bbfc25a48846ea436aa715ad3",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 5.758548752834467,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 142
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "The regression that broke subagent skill use is gone.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c6aece35617d0a19ed17d33c487286c79885f2b62bf75886b546ff3754e61c71",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 157
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "If you build with subagents, this one alone is worth the update.",
      "checksum": "sha256:735437e8a9c15d0d1bed80cd39e6e5ce270e5a7519cbc16272467cab6787fb49",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 166
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Fifth. The refresh token race that wiped shared credentials is patched. Parallel sessions no longer dead end at four oh one after a refresh.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b1e81aeefc36d15670a3b289a0c3f090887e49ef99c2726371dba9f199b1f545",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 9.984580498866213,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 178
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "If you run multiple agents at once, this fix is the headline.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9fadd81456b4652c95929172fffde63088eb08be222632501974668d3f1d9a18",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 202
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Sixth. The one hour prompt cache T T L was being silently downgraded to five minutes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5ef52ecc4ce780664522b66ad23bd0738a854c32cb83d9a1afbb638c71e80ba5",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 5.61922902494331,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 214
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Now honored. ENABLE PROMPT CACHING ONE H actually does what it says.",
      "checksum": "sha256:17b57794e1ef3e784f4ad2cbaaa53f0f9a946532ad9c6f382b8c260d86bc1929",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 5.479909297052155,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 230
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Which patch made your day? Drop a comment below.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f6ba9155b932f1d0edfbd6b69321583dff8aa4476aba4f42fc4c27dfb9765dcf",
